projects.name: Maternity Health and Child HealthCare
projects.description: Developed an inclusive maternity and child healthcare platform to support single mothers living away from family. Created a compassionate Chatbot to provide reassurance and answer pregnancy-related questions. Designed a website with tailored diet plans, exercise routines, and monthly guidance to promote a healthy pregnancy journey. Implemented emergency doctor locator services and facilitated video therapy sessions for emotional support. Provided comprehensive post-delivery child care tips to help new mothers confidently care for their newborns.

projects.name: Seq to Seq Translation Model: [Research Paper]
projects.description: Researched sequence-to-sequence models with attention layers for machine translation. Enhanced translation accuracy by optimizing the attention mechanism to focus on relevant input sequences. Evaluated model performance on diverse datasets to improve translation quality and efficiency.
